Mbishop initially stole the hearts of many South Africans during his audition in the first episode of season 12.He had the judges and viewers in stitches when he opted for "classical'' singing in an attempt to become South Africa's idol.While he might not have won the singing competition, he managed to walk away with a wooden mic and also got to share a stage with Somizi.The two gave one of the most sidesplitting performances that had us rolling on the floor with laughter.If you didn't catch it live on TV, brace yourself... 